snippet.title: Zelda: Twilight Princess' Strangest Mystery… Solved?
snippet.description:
Twilight Princess HD features mysterious carvings on the walls of Castle Town, including characters that should be impossible. But recently, a development give us more information on the origins of these carvings.

►EvanD0's post: https://www.reddit.com/r/zelda/comments/h9tty6/tphd_jack_kirby_crosby_clears_up_why_a_new_mural/
